{"tid":879890,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分享吓自己脫毒既經驗","createTime":"2018-10-28T10:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T11:44:26.000Z","uid":198320,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0adf284e5060aa1388f53a2283ada5287d0f82f8","tid":879890,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"毒呢種氣質我從中學開始就有 係我入左男校後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n六年既生活對女性變得好抗拒 甚至果時會係到諗咩呢個世界完來有女仔啊，除左老母 我都無機會同女性講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打扮就自然係兩三日洗一次頭啦 當時覺得好理所當然 簡番副粗框眼鏡黑識既 兩三個月剪一次頭 每次都剪到77地果隻 除左校服 出街格仔衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來讀完中學開始了解到有異性既存在 但都仍然係好被動果隻<br />\n開始學識打扮<br />\n<br />\n首先每日洗兩次頭<br />\n衫其實唔太緊要 但唔好太7 頭反而緊要d<br />\n剪頭髮要有要求 我都係經歷左好多次先剪得好<br />\n咁樣唔會有人會覺得你係毒撚<br />\n最後最緊要就係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n你地都得啊"},{"pid":"748114d86bc7eb4a9144920aca876ada90a71a65","tid":879890,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae2e66417a77b84516bc7ce4bb5f515a947b8b94","t